name: English Underground
description: Countercultural scene in the United Kingdom, centred around London clubs like UFO and Middle Earth, which peaked in 1966 and 1967.

children.name: Ladbroke Grove Scene
children.description: English Underground scene which blossomed in Ladbroke Grove, London, soon after the closure of the popular West End psychedelic club Middle Earth in 1968; faded by the mid-'70s, especially following the rise of Pub Rock and Punk.
